comment_data.body:
Seems that we return API key as string in the response. But I think it is better to return in a json like this:
```json
{
    apiKey: $onDemandAPIKey
}
```

So, we can add additional info in the future like expire time, etc ...
I think, this should be error level log.
backend api will returns data in this format
